Text:
Chloe from Met-Art has always been an interesting one.  Her body is AWESOME, and her attractiveness is acceptable.  But there's something missing about her.

This is a very old set. :)  I would download, but I already have it, many times over.
This torrent has every known photo of Chloe that is out there.  There is no more!  Sorry, I wish there were more too.
Virus scan detected a possible virus in one of the photos, be warned
According to my vault log it was 'Chloe\Saint Tropez\MET-ART_dm_54_0013.jpg'
